<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٦٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6014">مَحْمُودٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2386">سَعِيدُ بْنُ عَامِرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7242">يُونُسَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1389">الْحَسَنِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6594">أَبِي بَكْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«انْكَسَفَتِ الشَّمْسُ عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>، فَصَلَّى رَكْعَتَيْنِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>